      <h1 style="margin-top:18px">A &euro;1M seed round for Parkinson&rsquo;s <em>care &amp; research</em>.</h1>
    </div>
    <p class="lead" style="margin-top:22px">Koios Care secures a &euro;1M seed round to bring AI and digital biomarkers to Parkinson&rsquo;s disease care and research.</p>
